<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="rv-hero text-center">
    <h1 class="fw-bold">About Red Village</h1>
    <p class="rv-sub mx-auto">Zimbabwe's creative marketplace — built for the makers, the musicians, and the fans who love them.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
      <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold">What we do</h2>
      <p>Red Village is a creative marketplace built for Zimbabwean talent. We connect
        DJs, visual artists, photographers, videographers, curators, designers, and
        editors with the audiences and buyers who love their work — from Harare's
        studios to the festival stage.</p>
      <p>Makers run their own storefronts inside shared malls, sell products and tickets,
        and publish their portfolios. Fans discover events, browse galleries, and stream
        local music, all in one place.</p>
      <%= link_to "Meet our creators", "/creators", class: "btn btn-rv mt-2" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div class="row text-center g-3">
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="rv-stat p-4">
            <div class="rv-stat-num"><%= @stats[:stores] %></div>
            <div class="text-muted small">Stores</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="rv-stat p-4">
            <div class="rv-stat-num"><%= @stats[:events] %></div>
            <div class="text-muted small">Events</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="rv-stat p-4">
            <div class="rv-stat-num"><%= @stats[:artists] %></div>
            <div class="text-muted small">Artists</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="rv-stat p-4">
            <div class="rv-stat-num"><%= @stats[:creators] %></div>
            <div class="text-muted small">Creators</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12">
      <div class="rv-section-head">
        <h2 class="rv-gradient-text">How it works</h2>
        <hr class="rv-rule">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
      <div class="card rv-card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="h5 card-title"><i class="fas fa-store text-purple me-2" style="color:#a730b2;"></i>Open a store</h3>
          <p class="card-text text-muted">Set up a storefront inside one of our malls and list your products, tracks, and art.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
      <div class="card rv-card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="h5 card-title"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-2" style="color:#d34d94;"></i>Run events</h3>
          <p class="card-text text-muted">Publish events, sell tickets, and share your line-ups with the community.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
      <div class="card rv-card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="h5 card-title"><i class="fas fa-users me-2" style="color:#ff1493;"></i>Build a following</h3>
          <p class="card-text text-muted">Grow your audience with a public profile, portfolio, and gallery of your work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
